'''尚-皮耶·達胡桑'''（{{lang-fr|'''Jean-Pierre Darroussin'''}}，{{bd|1953年|12月4日|catIdx=D}}）是法國男演員、導演和編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&documentID=66589|title=Premonition premieres to applause for Darroussin|date=1 September 2006|work=Cineuropa|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104003031/http://cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&documentID=66589|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他曾以《{{fr-link|歡樂家庭晚餐|Un air de famille (film, 1996)}}》獲得[[凯撒电影奖|凱薩電影獎]]最佳男配角。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wikinfo.org/wiki.phtml?title=C%E9sar_Award_for_Best_Actor_in_a_Supporting_Role |title=César Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2012-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120716181122/http://www.wikinfo.org/wiki.phtml?title=C%E9sar_Award_for_Best_Actor_in_a_Supporting_Role |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

